56361,"title":"圆桌上 100 个人轮流开枪，最可能活下来的是几号？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/8225556361","type":"question","created":1735510119,"answer_count":54,"follower_count":364,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1291,1771,7050,8145,137155],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"圆桌上有 1 到 100 号，1 号右手边是 2 号，左手边是 100 号。1 号在左轮手枪的六个弹槽中放入一颗子弹，任意旋转转轮之后，关上转轮。开枪打 2 号，如果 2 号未中弹，把枪交给 2 号，反之交给 3 号， 3 号重复以上操作后，如果 4 号未中弹，把枪交给 4 号，反之交给 5 号。最后一个人命中 1 号或把枪交给 1 号，继续循环。最后留下来的最可能是几号？ 相关问题：圆桌上 1000 个人轮流开枪，最后活下来的是几号？"},"attached_info":"CkEI492kgMiko7ANEAMaCTExMjYyMTQ1MCDnkMe7BjAAOOwCQBJyCjgyMjU1NTYzNjF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"38 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-e9e42ed6bfc24d5cfcd25cc97098611a_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"19_1736211392.567759","card_id":"Q_54338688","target":{"id":54338688,"title":"倪永孝为什么要杀四个大佬？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/54338688","type":"question","created":1483408495,"answer_count":145,"follower_count":1191,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[68,8385,20879,20995,98022],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"倪永孝当时应该已经知道杀他父亲的是韩琛老婆，为何还要杀另外四个大佬？就因为这四个大佬在倪坤死的那一晚有过反水的念头吗？这五个大佬如果一起死了之后谁来替倪家做事呢？"},"attached_info":"Cj4I492kgMiko7ANEAMaCDEzOTU1NDI4IO+IrMMFMAA4pwlAE3IINTQzMzg2ODh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"21 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-35b838ed9e678714645ce14bf3295867_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"20_1736211392.568192","card_id":"Q_7286109372","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v